{
  "stem": "11744.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when we were taking message we always had somebody down on the sidewalk going back and forth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If they saw that car they would run up there, stop it, and so we would stop taking the message.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But many people have been arrested because they were found taking those message.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we were always given the instruction that we were told, for instance, that they were going to send a-- a parachute with-- with armaments, and we were told where the parachute would-- would come down.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we'd just go and pick it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sometime in our four years of fight against the Germans, they were there before we were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it also happened that we were getting parts of a machine gun, for instance, in one shipment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the other part would come in a second shipment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they would get hold of a second shipment, so you would never could make a real machine gun.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was the life we had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, there was no such a thing as getting orders from anybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was much later, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At the time of liberation, then there was a captain and a general and a-- but all the time during the war, it was-- there was nothing like this.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was hit and miss, try to do things as much as you can.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could-- we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got message-- well, we got message from the BBC.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the way-- that's the way we were getting orders, and we never could know otherwise.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you had no idea how people got arrested.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My husband met a friend of his one day in a cafe in Lyon, which is a very big city in France.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
